== 製作 ==
=== 發展 ===
2012年3月17日，雷利·史考特表示在《[[普罗米修斯_(电影)|普罗米修斯]]》留下許多未被解決的問題，可能會在續集裡解答「如果我們夠幸運有第二部的話，影片的確留給了你一些很好的懸而未決的問題。」<ref name="Sequel2">{{cite web |first=Dave |last=Trumbore |title=WonderCon 2012: Prometheus Panel Recap Featuring Sir Ridley Scott and Damon Lindelof |url=http://collider.com/prometheus-wondercon/152633/ |publisher=Collider.com |work= |date=2012-03-17 |accessdate=2012-03-18 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/68TNtGacr?url=http://collider.com/prometheus-wondercon/152633/ |archivedate=2012-06-16 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref name="Sequel1">{{cite news | last=Kit | first=Borys | url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/wondercon-2012-ridley-scott-prometheus-extended-trailer-301378 | title=WonderCon 2012: Ridley Scott Talks 'Prometheus' As Extended Trailer Debuts (Video) | publisher=[[Prometheus_Global_Media|Prometheus Global Media]] | work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] | date=2011-03-17 | accessdate=2012-03-18 | archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/68QMH9lR0?url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/wondercon-2012-ridley-scott-prometheus-extended-trailer-301378 | archivedate=2012-06-14 | deadurl=no }}</ref>面对续集是否会是《异形》直接相关前传的问题，[[戴蒙·林道夫|戴蒙·林道夫]]回答：“如果我们有幸制作续集的话……它会和原本的《异形》距离更远。”<ref name="MiscWonderCon12">{{cite web |first=Christina |last=Radish |title=Director Ridley Scott, Writer Damon Lindelof and Michael Fassbender Talk Prometheus at WonderCon 2012 |url=http://collider.com/ridley-scott-damon-lindelof-michael-fassbender-prometheus-interview/153243/ |publisher=Collider.com |work= |date=2012-03-18 |accessdate=2012-03-18 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/68TNq5dm1?url=http://collider.com/ridley-scott-damon-lindelof-michael-fassbender-prometheus-interview/153243/ |archivedate=2012-06-16 |deadurl=no }}</ref>2012年6月，林道夫称本片中有些剧情元素是故意不解釋的，以便在续集中给出答案，他和斯科特已经深入讨论了解决方案，使《普罗米修斯》即使没有续集也可以成为一部独立的作品<ref name="Sequel4">{{cite news | last=Gilchrist | first=Todd | url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/prometheus-damon-lindelof-sequel-ridley-scott-paradise-332875 | title='Prometheus' Writer Damon Lindelof on Rumored Sequel 'Paradise' and Whether He's the Man to Write It | publisher=Prometheus Global Media | work=The Hollywood Reporter | date=2012-06-05 | accessdate=2012-06-05 | archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/68QMKiIht?url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/prometheus-damon-lindelof-sequel-ridley-scott-paradise-332875 | archivedate=2012-06-14 | deadurl=no }}</ref>。斯科特称，续集将跟随伊莉莎白·蕭前往她的下一个目的地：“因为要是那就是天堂，天堂就不可能是你所想像的那个样子。天堂的内涵是极端险恶和不详的。”林道夫觉得自己有可能不会参与续集的制作，但他也表示，如果斯科特希望某个项目有他的参与，那他会很难拒绝。同时他还认为《普罗米修斯》有从創新的构思或创意中获益<ref name="Sequel6">{{cite web |first=Adam |last=Chitwood |title=Prometheus Sequel Recap: What We Know About the Possible Follow-Up So Far |url=http://collider.com/prometheus-2-sequel/172444/ |publisher=Collider.com |work= |date=2012-06-11 |accessdate=2012-06-12 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131111065706/http://collider.com/prometheus-2-sequel/172444/ |archivedate=2013-11-11 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。斯科特表示，还需要有一部额外的电影来說明《普罗米修斯》的续集和《异形》之间的差距。<ref name="Sequel7">{{cite web|url=http://downloads.bbc.co.uk/podcasts/fivelive/kermode/kermode_20120601-1008a.mp3|title=Sir Ridley Scott, 01 June 12|author=Scott, Ridley|publisher=[[BBC_Online|BBC Online]]|quote=Yeah, it's not the same planet at all. No. If there was a sequel to this, which there might be if the film is successful, there'll be two more of these before you even get to ''Alien 1''.|date=2012-06-01|accessdate=2012-06-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131110183808/http://downloads.bbc.co.uk/podcasts/fivelive/kermode/kermode_20120601-1008a.mp3|archive-date=2013-11-10|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

2012年8月1日，福克斯公司打算拍摄续集，斯科特、拉佩斯和法斯賓達都将回归，并且正在與新的编剧商谈，以便在林道夫不能回归时接替。影片预计至少要到2014年才会上映。<ref name="Sequel8">{{cite news | last=McClintock | first=Pamela | url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/summer-movie-franchise-avengers-snow-white-magic-mike-356583 | title=Summer's Studio Smackdown: From 'Men in Black 3' to 'Prometheus,' Which Franchises Will Get Another Chapter | publisher=Prometheus Global Media | work=The Hollywood Reporter | date=2012-08-01 | accessdate=2012-08-01 | archive-date=2012-08-03 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120803005049/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/summer-movie-franchise-avengers-snow-white-magic-mike-356583 | dead-url=no }}</ref>2012年12月19日，林道夫由于已经接下了其他工作而决定不参与本片续集的制作。<ref name="SequelDec2012">{{cite web |first=Steve |last=Weintraub |title=Exclusive: Damon Lindelof Is Not Writing the Prometheus Sequel; Explains Why |url=http://collider.com/prometheus-sequel-damon-lindelof/219084/ |publisher=Collider.com |work= |date=2012-12-19 |accessdate=2012-12-20 |archive-date=2013-10-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131010002355/http://collider.com/prometheus-sequel-damon-lindelof/219084/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>2013年6月，正在进行与杰克·裴格伦（{{lang|en|Jack Paglen}}）担任续集编剧的谈判<ref name="SequelJun2013">{{cite news |first=Justin |last=Kroll |url=http://variety.com/2013/film/news/transcendence-scribe-to-pen-prometheus-sequel-1200478483/ |title=‘Prometheus’ Sequel Moving Forward at Fox |publisher=PMC |work=Variety |date=2013-06-17 |accessdate=2013-06-19 |archive-date=2013-11-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131115005457/http://variety.com/2013/film/news/transcendence-scribe-to-pen-prometheus-sequel-1200478483/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> 。2013年10月，斯科特确认剧本已经完成。<ref name="SequelOct2013">{{cite news|first=Ann|last=Lee|url=http://metro.co.uk/2013/10/27/ridley-scott-confirms-prometheus-2-is-still-on-the-way-4162956/|title=Ridley Scott confirms Prometheus 2 is still on the way|publisher=dmg media|work=Metro|date=2013-10-27|accessdate=2013-10-27|archive-date=2013-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131030054538/http://metro.co.uk/2013/10/27/ridley-scott-confirms-prometheus-2-is-still-on-the-way-4162956/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="SequelOct2013B">{{cite web |first=Hugh |last=Armitage |url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/movies/news/a527586/prometheus-2-script-is-finished-says-ridley-scott.html |title='Prometheus 2' script is finished, says Ridley Scott |publisher=Hearst Corporation |work=Digital Spy |date=2013-10-30 |accessdate=2013-10-30 |archive-date=2013-11-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131101174908/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/movies/news/a527586/prometheus-2-script-is-finished-says-ridley-scott.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>2014年3月，[[麥可·葛林_(編劇)|麥可·葛林]]正受聘重写裴格伦的剧本，續集預定於2014年年底拍攝，2016年3月4日上映，<ref name="SequelMar14A">{{cite news |first=Jeff |last=Sneider |url=http://www.thewrap.com/prometheus-2-lands-green-lantern-writer-may-feature-multiple-michael-fassbenders-exclusive/ |title=‘Prometheus 2' Lands ‘Green Lantern’ Writer; May Feature Multiple Michael Fassbenders (Exclusive) |publisher=The Wrap |date=2014-03-24 |accessdate=2014-03-24 |archive-date=2014-03-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140324235825/http://www.thewrap.com/prometheus-2-lands-green-lantern-writer-may-feature-multiple-michael-fassbenders-exclusive/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="SequelMar14B">{{cite web |first=Adam |last=Chitwood |title=Ridley Scott To Next Direct Prometheus Sequel For March 4, 2016 Release; Filming Begins This Fall |url=http://collider.com/prometheus-2-release-date/ |publisher=Collider.com |work= |date=2014-03-24 |accessdate=2014-03-24 |archive-date=2014-03-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140324235948/http://collider.com/prometheus-2-release-date/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>預計在澳洲福斯製片廠開拍。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Picard|first1=Chris|title=Ridley Scott Currently Scouting Filming Locations for Prometheus 2 in Australia?|url=http://www.scified.com/site/prometheusmovies/ridley-scott-currently-scouting-filming-locations-for-prometheus-2-in-australia|accessdate=2014-07-05|publisher=scified.com|date=2014-05-22|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140627031323/http://www.scified.com/site/prometheusmovies/ridley-scott-currently-scouting-filming-locations-for-prometheus-2-in-australia|archivedate=2014-06-27|deadurl=yes}}</ref>9月4日，史考特對於《普羅米修斯》的續集，他個人是充滿期望。當初許多第一集的負評，都指出缺少了觀眾熟悉的太空怪物。史考特表示“怪物已經是過去式。老調無需重彈。”<ref>{{cite news|last1=Falk|first1=Ben|title=Ridley Scott Updates Us On Prometheus 2 And Blade Runner Sequel|url=https://uk.yahoo.com/movies/ridley-scott-updates-us-on-prometheus-2-and-blade-98235330841.html|accessdate=2014-09-26|publisher=yahoo.com|date=2014-09-24|archive-date=2014-09-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140926025959/https://uk.yahoo.com/movies/ridley-scott-updates-us-on-prometheus-2-and-blade-98235330841.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2015年8月17日{{tsl|en|Bloody Disgusting|Bloody Disgusting}}報導[[尼爾·布洛姆坎普|尼爾·布洛姆坎普]]執導的《異形5》將會延期至《普羅米修斯2》上映之後才開始製作。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Barkan|first1=Jonathan|title=Is ‘Prometheus’ Holding Up Neill Blomkamp’s ‘Alien’? (Exclusive)|url=http://bloody-disgusting.com/news/3357432/blomkamps-alien-happening-youre-going-patient/|accessdate=2015-08-19|work=bloody-disgusting.com|date=2015-08-17|archive-date=2015-08-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150819013514/http://bloody-disgusting.com/news/3357432/blomkamps-alien-happening-youre-going-patient/|dead-url=no}}</ref>9月24日，史考特證實電影名稱為《異形：失樂園》。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Han|first1=Angie|title=Ridley Scott Announces New ‘Prometheus 2′ Title|url=http://www.slashfilm.com/prometheus-2-title/|website=/Film|accessdate=2015-09-24|archive-date=2015-09-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150926012316/http://www.slashfilm.com/prometheus-2-title/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2015年11月，斯科特透露了電影新的命名《異形：聖約》，並預計2016年2月在澳洲開拍。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Perez|first1=Rodrigo|title=Ridley Scott Says 'Alien: Paradise Lost' Will Now Be Called ‘Alien: Covenant’|url=http://blogs.indiewire.com/theplaylist/ridley-scott-says-alien-paradise-lost-will-be-now-called-alien-covenant-20151113|accessdate=2015-11-15|work=indiewire.com|date=2015-11-13|archive-date=2017-12-31|archive-url=https://archive.is/20171231002011/http://www.indiewire.com/2015/11/ridley-scott-says-alien-paradise-lost-will-now-be-called-alien-covenant-104744/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2015年11月16日發表了官方標示，简介及上映日期。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Chitwood|first1=Adam|title=‘Prometheus’ Sequel Gets Release Date and Synopsis, But Where’s Noomi Rapace?|url=http://collider.com/prometheus-2-release-date-synopsis-noomi-rapace/|accessdate=2015-11-16|work=Collider|date=2015-11-16|archive-date=2015-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151117152523/http://collider.com/prometheus-2-release-date-synopsis-noomi-rapace/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2015年12月史考特接受[[The_Wrap|The Wrap]]採訪表示《異形：聖約》裡会收录艺术家[[H·R·吉格爾|H·R·吉格爾]]为影片创作的经典异形卵形象。“影片里会包含他们所有，异形蛋，抱脸异形，破胸异形，以及成熟异形。”斯科特還表示“影片中的主角将去往工程师诞生的星球，他们会遇到那些由他们所创造的先进生物生化人。他们为什么会创造出这些野兽？它们是生物机械人，像一种武器。电影会解释这些问题，同时会重新引进异形。”<ref>{{cite news|last1=Pond|first1=Steve|title=Ridley Scott Talks Humor in ‘The Martian,’ Dishes on ‘Alien’ Prequels|url=http://www.thewrap.com/ridley-scott-martian-humor-prometheus-alien-prequel/|accessdate=2015-12-12|work=thewrap.com|date=2015-12-11|archive-date=2015-12-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151213104150/http://www.thewrap.com/ridley-scott-martian-humor-prometheus-alien-prequel/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 前期製作 ===
2015年8月，史考特證實他開始為影片進行勘景<ref>{{cite web|title=Inside The Martian: Empire Meets NASA|url=http://www.empireonline.com/features/the-martian-at-NASA|accessdate=2015-08-30|work=empireonline.com|archive-date=2015-09-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150905055006/http://www.empireonline.com/features/the-martian-at-NASA|dead-url=no}}</ref>，2015年10月，澳洲政府表示《[[雷神索爾3：諸神黃昏|雷神索爾3：諸神黃昏]]》和《異形：聖約》將於2016年在澳洲開拍，並且為電影計畫提供總計4725萬澳幣（約3400萬美金）的資金。<ref>{{cite news|title=Australia Secures Two Blockbuster Films|url=http://foreignminister.gov.au/releases/Pages/2015/jb_mr_151022c.aspx?w=tb1CaGpkPX%2FlS0K%2Bg9ZKEg%3D%3D|accessdate=2015-10-22|work=foreignminister.gov.au|date=2015-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160412104956/http://foreignminister.gov.au/releases/Pages/2015/jb_mr_151022c.aspx?w=tb1CaGpkPX%2FlS0K%2Bg9ZKEg%3D%3D|archive-date=2016-04-12|dead-url=yes}}</ref>2016年3月28日，20世纪福克斯公司的子公司沃兹制作有限公司，前往了[[紐西蘭|紐西蘭]][[蒂阿瑙|蒂阿瑙]]進行场地视察並且在[[菲奧德蘭|菲奧德蘭]]進行拍攝<ref>{{cite news | last = Mack | first = Ben | title = Has Alien: Covenant landed in Fiordland | url = http://www.stuff.co.nz/entertainment/78345810/has-alien-covenant-landed-in-fiordland | accessdate = 2016-03-29 | work = Stuff.co.nz | date = 2016-03-30 | archive-date = 2019-01-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190119231931/https://www.stuff.co.nz/entertainment/78345810/has-alien-covenant-landed-in-fiordland | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

