-01-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160109172729/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/ridley-scott-alien-covenant-is-844051 |dead-url=no }}</ref>；並表示《普羅米修斯》的續集將揭示是誰創造了異形<ref>{{cite web |url=http://uk.ign.com/articles/2015/11/11/ridley-scott-says-prometheus-sequels-will-reveal-who-created-aliens |title=Ridley Scott Says Prometheus Sequels Will Reveal Who Created Aliens |first1=Chris |last1=Tilly |first2=Leigh |last2=Singer |work=IGN |date=2015-11-11 |accessdate=2017-05-10 |archive-date=2020-05-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200529063544/https://www.ign.com/articles/2015/11/11/ridley-scott-says-prometheus-sequels-will-reveal-who-created-aliens |dead-url=no }}</ref>。第三部前傳片的劇本是在《異形：聖約》的製作期間所撰寫的，於2017年完成，計劃於2018年開始製作<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.smh.com.au/entertainment/movies/ridley-scott-promises-a-return-to-alienstyle-horror-in-alien-covenant-20170222-guj8wk.html|title=Ridley Scott promises a return to Alien-style horror in Alien: Covenant|first=Garry|last=Maddox|date=2017-03-03|publisher=|via=The Sydney Morning Herald|accessdate=2017-05-10|archive-date=2017-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170305112813/http://www.smh.com.au/entertainment/movies/ridley-scott-promises-a-return-to-alienstyle-horror-in-alien-covenant-20170222-guj8wk.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2017年4月，史考特宣布，《異形5》永遠不會推出<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/film/2017/may/02/ridley-scott-alien-5-covenant-neill-blomkamp|title=Ridley Scott: Neill Blomkamp's Alien 5 is never going to happen|last=Pulver|first=Andrew|date=2017-05-02|work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]|accessdate=2017-05-05|archive-date=2017-05-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170504233043/https://www.theguardian.com/film/2017/may/02/ridley-scott-alien-5-covenant-neill-blomkamp|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

